events.name: Cloud Study Jam - Machine Learning

group.name: GDG Cloud Twin Cities - A Google Developer Group

events.description:
Get training from an official chapter of Google Developer Group, a $55+ value, free of charge. Together we'll work through several Google Cloud labs. You will get hands-on experience with Machine Learning in the Google Cloud: From working with TensorFlow to the new AutoML.

Then after our live session, you will have free access to more labs you can finish at home. Complete all labs in the quest and earn a Google-hosted badge for your online profile, and additional 30 days access to the training platform to complete any labs you want.

Agenda:
9:30 AM - 10.00 AM: Registration, Introduction
10.00 AM - 10.30 AM: Understanding the Platform Basics
10.30 AM - 12.00 PM: Hands-on Labs Starts
12.00 PM - 12.30 PM: Lunch Break
12.30 PM - 2.00 PM: Hands-on Lab and wrap-up
2.00 PM - 2.30 PM : Snacks and Networking, Group Photograph

Please Note: As this event is a hands-on session, attendees must bring their own laptop and chargers. You will be able to earn Google Badges and Certificates.

Venue:
Agosto
420 N 5th St #400,
Minneapolis, MN 55401
events.how_to_find_us: We'll be in the main presentation room, just inside the 4th floor Agosto entrance.
